text:
I truly enjoy the assistance of Roomba.  No doubt, it saves me lots of time and does a relatively great job.

A couple of suggestions:
- the front of Roomba is black and it tends to leave marks on my baseboard.  I purchased a book tape which works great applied to the front of Roomba (the lover front; not covering the sensors); I change the tape every so often;

- Roomba plays a sound when job is completed; that sound for some reason does not play on my iPad;  only a visual announcement appears on a screen; a sound for Roomba on my iPad is selected in my settings but it does not play;
- I wish every Roomba, no matter what series, would be able to clean a particular room; I purchased two towers to block Roomba from entering rooms without doors, however, it would be convenient not to have to set out the towers to clean only selected rooms.

Ewa
